Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:22.67,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.13,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Then,}Vậy thì
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.54,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{after he placed the ring on my ring finger...}sau khi bác ấy đeo chiếc nhẫn vào ngón tay cô thì...
