Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.55,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, whatever! I finally made it halfway through, so I'll cut to the chase!}Mà thôi chắc kệ đi! Dù gì em cũng nói gần hết rồi, nên em nói phần cuối lun nha anh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.29,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{In short...}Nói cách khác...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.29,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{I love you!}Em yêu anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.52,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{That was long enough as it was.}Bấy nhiêu đó cũng đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.20,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{How much more did you have planned?}Cô còn tính nói gì thêm nữa sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:29.84,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm just... in love with you... Mahiro...}Em chỉ.... yêu mỗi anh thôi.... Mahrio-san...
