Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.29,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{you'd be in danger, too.}thì cô cũng sẽ bị liên lụy theo luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.78,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{So... it was for me?}Vậy... là vì em à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.11,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Well, yeah, I guess.}Ừ, tôi đoán là vậy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.58,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Just... for me?}Chỉ.... vì em?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.91,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{I wouldn't go that far.}Đừng có nhắc lại nhiều lần thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.54,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{It was for you.}Đó là vì cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:33.25,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Mahiro... do you... like me?}Mahiro-san... anh có.... thích em không?
